Okay. Hm.

 

Tomorrow is Jon and my 7th month anniversary!! I'm so f-in happy!

 

Dude... Jon scared me so bad today when he got home from his dad's... This is the dialogue.

 

J: Hey, I just want to say something. You may not be happy, but when I was at the football game, I... Didn't watch it much...

S: W-What...?

J: I went to go get something to eat, and I bumped into my ex-gf. Literally.

S: I... I...

J: So... We, uhm...

S: Y-Yes..?

J: Talked in the parking lot a lot.

 

At first I thought that he said that he had made out with her.. I was so scared, but it made me feel better when he told me that they just talked. But... for some reason, it still is riding heavy on my heart. Why? I have no clue...

 

Hm...

Sarah

I'M LEAVING TOMORROW!! How awesome is that?! I've done so much in the past few weeks, it's crazy. I've gone to Kayla's house, Kayla's dad's, East Rochester for a weekened, Six Flags, Nashua, Shopping in Portsmouth, went to Hampton Beach, got a wicked burn, and a bunch of other stuff. This has been a wicked month...

Man, I'm going to miss you all when I leave. I shall be thinking of you all when I'm gone.

I got a wicked sunburn on mah legs. I didn't know that I could get burned on my legs! yea yea, I'm smart, huh?

 

I'm leaving in two days for three weeks, so this iz gunna need some MAJOR updating when I return! haha! I'm going to France, Italy, and Spain for three weeks with the Student Ambassador program. Greatness! I'm going with some of the coolest peeps in the entire world. I love them to bits... but it hurts to leave my bf...

 

~*~HugZ 'n' KisseZ~*~

~*~Sarah~*~

Leaving in four days, I'm so excited! I can't wait to get this thing started, but who knows what will happen! How much fun will I have? Only a select few will know... Only they will get postcards. HAHAHAHHAHAAHA! I'm so weird. I love how I can be myself around my friends, and not worry what they think. Muahaha!

Tomorrow I am probably going with Jon, his sister, and step-sister to Hampton Beach! How fun! I hope I don't burn. Dad says that a sunburn and a plane do NOT mix. Oh well, means Jon can put sunblock on my back and shoulders! ^_~

I love Jon so much, it's crazy. I know I've said this about guys before, but I fell as though I could spend the rest of my life together with this guy! He's... perfect!

 

~*~Sarah~*~

lol omg omg omg! Jon used a big word! Enthused! lol I love doing that to him. It's fun. He doesn't like to use big words, so when he does, I rub it in. lmao I <3 it.

 

I <3 JON!! He's my baby. I figured the whole, ex situation thing out, so I'm happy. I am so glad I didn't do something that I would have regretted with the other... I love Jon...

 

 

Muah

HI! What's uuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuup?! lmao I'm so friggen hyper right now... hehehe... I'm talking to my baby on the phone... he's so hawt... I lurve him! ^_^

 

Sarah

O....my..... god.... I AM SO BORED!!! It's vacation, yet I'm bored out of my miiiiiiiiiiiiiiind! Why do I have to live in the middle of nowhere?!?!?!?!



ACK!

... I am currently not in a great mood. Matt, my bf, broke up with me yesterday. It was out of the blue. Well... not really... I've been half expecting this for quite some time now. I just can't believe that it happened... I loved him with every fiber of my being, and the sad thing is is that I STILL do. I just wish that he could take me back, and everything would be alright again....

Things have been happening lately that I cannot explain. My bf hasn't been returning my calls, and he didn't even call me on our two month. I want to go to the movies today so I can see him, but... ::Sigh:: I'm scared that I won't be able to see him until Thursday... or talk to him for that matter...

"I don't want another pretty face

I don't want just anyone to hold

I don't want my love to go to waste

I want you and your beautiful soul"

 

I want him so badly, I want to stay with him forever...

"your hands with their velvety feel

makes my head spin

your lips such luscious lips

makes my head spin

your body your amazing body

makes my head spin

very moment with you

every amazing moment with you

makes my head spin

o lay with you

would be the sweetest sin

being with you

makes my head spin

to cuddle with you

makes my head spin

to be near you

makes my head spin

you make my head spin

everything about you

every beautiful thing about you

makes my head spin

to lay with you

would be the the sweetest sin.

everything about you

makes my head spin

and makes me want to sin

you are my sin and I love it that way." -Alexander-

Matt, that's to you... I love you.

Alrighty then. Time to fill people in on my life! ^_^ 

 

I am now dating Matt. He is sooo sweet! I love him to bits. Corey... just made me feel uncomfortable. But oh well. It's over now, and in the past.

I talked to Melissa the other day. She sounds so cool! I miss her so much, it's not even funny. She NEEDS to come up to my house lol. I said so. lol

 

Well, gotta go for a little. Tired.

Sarah

Well.... I made things a bunch easier. I broke up with Corey. Yes yes, some people are probably going, "You did what!? So much about being in love with him!" But I don't care. He was making things waaaaay too hard, and I didn't want to deal with it. Way too much on my shoulders at once, and he was one thing I needed to push off. It may sound mean, but I'm glad I did. I feel relieved that everything's easier now.

 

>.>  <.<   >.>   To tell you the truth, I have my eyes on someone else now. He's so sweet, but I'm NOT saying his name. Now at least. ^_^

 

Well, I gotta get ready for the movies. I'm going with Matt. Buh byes!

 

Sarah

Why must everything be so damn hard? I mean, I'm dating this guy, yet... I'm starting to feel less and less for him each day. Not to mention, that I like this other guy who is really close to me... DAMNIT! I mean, the other guy, but my BF and I barely talk. Besides, the other day, he put his video games over me. I mean, I'm not trying to sound self-centered, but he's done it before, and I'm sick of it. I don't want to deal with it anymore, but I'm afraid to leave him... :'( Why must love be so hard? Like, what happens if I date the other guy, and he ends up being a bastard, and I want my BF back? What happens then? ::Sighs:: This is too hard...

 

I have way to much stuff on my mind, and I don't want to deal with it! Why can't there be a simple reason, or answer to these questions? But noooooo! They HAVE to be waaaay to hard! I want to cry, but both say they hate to see me as such... Well... only one of the two has seen me cry, and he seemed to get really depressed.

 

Come on God! Make things easier, please! At least, clear my mind so I can understand what to do and find a solution!

 

Sarah

Hi! Welcome! Once again, I am posting. Been a long time, ne? Well, sorry! I've been verrrrrrrrrrrrrrrry busy. What with doctors appointments, school stuff, etc.

 

Oh! Speaking of doctors appts, I had to have an endoscopy, a head CAT scan, an abdominal CAT scan, pleeeeenty of docs, blood tests, and other things a'coming. And guess what they found.... NOTHING! A little irritation, and soreness, but NOTHING!!! I was flipping out about the fact they did all that for nothing, but I guess that it's needed to be able to rule out that kind of thing, ne?

 

Hey, I need to go now, tired, and lots of stuff on my mind. Buh byes!

 

 

Sarah

Well well well. It appears that you have returned to read my life, as it were? Anyways, welcome.

My life has been alright for the most part. As you know, I have a boyfriend! His name is Corey Morini, and he is so sweet!! I love him so much.

Well, sorry for the short post, but I need to jet. Bye!

 

Sarah

Okay, this is pissing me off. Jake is all happy one moment, then gets all mad at me for nothing I did!!! I act the same as I normally do, and yet he says I've changed!!! HOW??! Tell me that!  My God, he's even dissed my parents! I will NOT stand for that! I don't care what anyone says, but I WILL figure this out! As long as it takes, I will figure a solution. Be it blocking him, talking to him and figuring it out.

Damnit... how come he can make me cry!?

 

My parents are saying that they want me to give up on trying to reach him... No. I will never give up...

Dude.... First kisses....

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

ROCK!!!

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Need I say more?!?!

Dear Journal.

I have to admit something.

 

I may get my first kiss tonight! I'm going to Youth Group, and since Corey is there... Things may happen. And no, I will not go any farther than that. I promise.

 

But I'm so excited!! My first real kiss!!! ^-^

 

Corey, hun, why weren't you home today? I wanted to call you.

 

Well, g2g. Chores, then Youth Group! ^-^ yay!

 

Love ya Corey!

Sarah

Heya!

I am soooooo bored! Dude, I'm talking to Corey and Matt D on the phone, and they were picking on me! So, my daddy stepped in and said, "Oh, you can't blame them Sarah. Between them, they MUST have at least half a brain between the two of them!" They were on speakerphone, and they were like, "OOOOH!!!" It was so funny!

Also, I'm dating Corey Morini! He is so sweet!! He protects me, takes care of me, and so on. We started around October 1st, and he is so kind! I love him!

 

C ya!

 

Arawna

Oh Heavenly Father...

I have a request for you... Please... I beg of you.. Please protect Charlie.. He's like my brother!! For as long as I can remember, he's been there. Always in my mind. And now, he's going to Iraq again.. I can't stand the thought that he's leaving!! Right when the bombing over there is the worst. If I could I would go to protect him.. But I can't.. But God, he's one of the closest things I have to an older brother... Please protect him!

If he dies Lord... I don't know what I'd do. He, Ryan, and all the rest of his family means so much to me, that I would snap.

 

He's leaving Friday. Damnit!! I CAN'T HAVE THIS NOW!! I already have way to much damn stress, and I can't take more!!

 

Protection

Lord I do not ask for money,

Lord I do not ask for love.

Lord I only ask protection,

From the holiness above.

 

Protect my family,

As I will pray,

All I need is protection,

For him each passing day.

 

He is my brother,

That's all I have to say.

Protect him my Lord,

And I shall pray.

I have an Alpha major problem... I think I love Jake, but I can't do another long distance relationship! I mean, with a LD, I geeeeeeeet....

  1. Pain from missing him,
  2. I'm not able to see him, and
  3. I just can't stand it.

Gah... I have no idea what to do... With a NEAR me bf, I get...

  1. I'm able to hold his hand,
  2. He's able to hug me,
  3. I'm able to see him A LOT more,
  4. And I'm able to actually go to the movies or so on with him!!!

Yes, there are more pros then cons, but still.. I am being tortured by my heart, and I can't stand it. I want to love somebody, and when I find him, I can't have him!! It's like God is testing me or something!!! Sometimes, it all builds up that I want to end it all, but... I don't. People keep me here...

 

 

Sarah

Alrighty then. Yesterday, I went to the yearbook staff meetings, and found out that I can't make it to ANY meetings! It's like... yeaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa...

 

Oh yea,  HAPPY BIRTHDAY KEN! DANCE AROUND! lol It's my friend Ken's birthday.  He's 18 now! Legal to drive! It's like... ::Nudge nudge:: Drive me home? lol

 

Tomorrow, we are having a going away party for Shaina since she's moving next week. I made cupcakes! ^^ I feel all proud. Well... Hannah Sears and I did. We made blueberry ones with red food coloring, and they came out pink! We were like, "KICK ASS MAN!" We also made cornmuffins, and dyed them blue... Well, okay. They came out green, but, it was fun! We didn't have any milk, so we had to go to my neighbors to borrow some... It was funny!

::rubs eyes:: I'm soooo tired. I have such a long day tomorrow! Garg! Oh well, I took on the responsibility when I signed up for class president ne? lol

 

I gotta go now. I have other journals to post at!! ^^

 

Arawna

Okay, this is nuts now. I barely ever posted in this thing, NOW LOOK AT ME! THREE DAYS IN A ROW!! Wahoooo!! Throw a party! Well... maybe not.

 

I have the straaaaaaaaaangest thing happening to me. I think I have a crush on a senior! It's like... NO! I want someone near me, yes, but someone around my age! He's like... 18! I promised myself, that I wouldn't fall for seniors... ::Sighs:: I guess it was too hard.. Okay, okay. Some of you are wondering why I'm saying this is strange, but it's because I usually fall for guys I can't have. But, this one seems to like me... It's like, whaaaaaaaaaaaaaat?

 

I've decided to go onto the yearbook staff. Well, at least, check it out. I mean, for all I know, I may hate it! This guy says that I am ahead of my class in looks, academics, and achievments. >.<  I'm like, to you, maybe. To others? Nooooo! I am faaaaaaaaaaaar behind many in looks, and am a mere freshmen in grades. Achivements? Maybe. Who knows.

Well, I need to go now. A revoir!

Arawna

I have good news, and bad news. The good news is, is that Jake and I made up!! Everything's all good between us now, and I'm so happy. I couldn't stand being mad at him. I didn't want to do anything at first... But, I have to say, even though I WAS mad, I did have a good time at the mall and my fashion show. Yes, I was in a fashion show, not a huge one, but a fashion show.

The bad news is... Is Jake AND Mat have the flu... And I, myself, have a cold. Gah..

 

 

HAHAHAHA! My daddy say Travis today (The guy who sexually harrased me) at Market Basket, and gave him SUCH  diiiiiirty look! I swear he must have cringed!  Dat's muh daddy!

 

Well, I gotta go, just posting so Kelz will be happy. Love yas sisshy!

Arawna

Alrighty. I figured everything out with Jake, and Megan! So basically....

 

 

....

 

 

 

....

 

 

ISH ALL GOOD IN DAH HOOD MUH HOME DAWG!! lmao sorry, had to. I am hyper now!

 

BEWARE THE EVIL CHIPMUNKS!!! RISE MY MINIONS!! ::Laughs hysterically as they swarm around me:: Okay, who just chewed on my foot?!? o.0?

 

Okay, I need to go now. I am waaaaaaay to hyper for my own good...   >.<

I'm in school now. I'm in my last class though, which is good because I am exhausted. PLUS, I get to go to the Rochester fair!!! I am so syked.

Jake did something that really hurt me the other day... How could you do that baby? I said that even though we aren't dating, that we'd still be each other's ONLY, and you broke that promise... Thanks Kelsey by the way, for telling me and not keeping me in the dark. I am very glad that you told me.

My parents are thinking that I am slipping into some sort of depression. I say, "YOU NOTICE NOW?!?!" I've been giving hints for like, EVER! Oh well...

Well, I gotta go now. I need to actually do some, work. Bah...

But, I must say. Jake, you made me cry for like, an HOUR last night.. We need to talk desperately.

 

 

Love to all my friends,

~!*SaRaH*!~

Okay, Jake! Jake is muh babii boi and I will always love him. No matter whom we date, marry, etc, we will always love each other.

Jake, you mean so much to me... You say I helped you stay on this earth, and that makes me smile. I love knowing that I can help you when you help me so dang much...I love you...

 

Arawna

Pain seems to be running rampant lately. My friends, my family, all are suffering right in front of my eyes. I don't know how to help them... And yet... Why do I try when I can barely keep my own life in check? Heh... It's a little hard ne? Helping others when you can't even help yourself. I know that now.

When I was little, I used to think that I could help everyone who needed it, with no consequences. I know that it's impossible to help everyone around me. A silly little girls dream I guess... I suppose I need to ditch it and start over.

Geez... why can't life be easy?! It used to be...

My mom is right. I have entered, along with my friends, "Hormone Happy Hour" which leads to a headache... :: Sighs::

Summer vacation is supposed to be fun ne? Well, mine isn't. I stay home all summer, and do CHORES. Fun fun. Makes me want to jump around with joy. I do chores all week, and how do I be repayed? Two words; I don't. All I would like to have as a payment is to go to GYG to see my friends, but NOOOOOOOOOOOO! 

It's my parents anniversary, and guess what! I CAN GO! I asked them, and they said that they will most definately bring me!!! ::Giggles and dances around:: I'm so happy now!!

Aria

(If I don't know you) MUAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA! WELCOME TO MY REALM! You are under my power!!! ::Tries to make you jump off of a cliff, but instead you ram into a telephone pole:: Oh well, close enough! ::Grins:: ::Spins around in circles:: COME MY CHIPMUNK MINIONS!! ::Chipmunks swarm around me:: ::Laughs idiotically:: Ok, Mountain Dew before you go to bed reeeeeeeeeally give you an after affect.

~Arawna~
I am so scared... PA was so far, and it's closer now... And so many people want to see me, and I mean, I want to see them too, but hey! It's scary!

It's been a while ne? Well, I TALK TO MY BABII BOI! ::Laughs;: Not really my bf, but a good friend. His name is Jake, and he is so sweet! He's 13, and lives in Illinois. So what if I might not see him? He's awesome!!!

This is becoming hard... not typing, but living. I mean, I don't consider myself very pretty, yet people tell me otherwise! About five guys want to date me, but I don't really want to date them or I can't... I was asked out earlier this week, and I said no. The guy's sweet and all, but not my type.

Well, I need to do my chores and take a shower. BBS!

 

 

Sarah
